              or unable to perform at their full capacity
            </li>
            <li class="leading-relaxed">
              <strong class="font-semibold text-blue-600">Workplace accidents and injuries</strong> - 
              Substance use significantly increases the risk of accidents, especially in safety-sensitive positions
            </li>
            <li class="leading-relaxed">
              <strong class="font-semibold text-blue-600">Increased healthcare costs</strong> - 
              Substance abuse is associated with higher medical expenses and insurance claims
            </li>
            <li class="leading-relaxed">
              <strong class="font-semibold text-blue-600">Negative workplace culture</strong> - 
              Unaddressed substance issues can damage team dynamics, trust, and morale
            </li>
            <li class="leading-relaxed">
              <strong class="font-semibold text-blue-600">Legal and liability issues</strong> - 
              Employers may face legal consequences if substance abuse leads to workplace incidents
            </li>
          </ul>
  
