            Frontline supervisors play a critical role in prevention and early intervention:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-8 space-y-2">
            <li class="leading-relaxed">
              Train supervisors to recognize potential signs of substance abuse
            </li>
            <li class="leading-relaxed">
              Provide clear guidelines on how to address performance issues that may be 
              related to substance use
            </li>
            <li class="leading-relaxed">
              Teach appropriate intervention techniques that focus on job performance 
              rather than making personal diagnoses
            </li>
            <li class="leading-relaxed">
              Ensure supervisors understand available resources for referring employees
            </li>
          </ul>
  
