            <li class="leading-relaxed">
              Develop clear return-to-work policies and agreements
            </li>
            <li class="leading-relaxed">
              Consider temporary modified duties when appropriate
            </li>
            <li class="leading-relaxed">
              Implement follow-up monitoring in a supportive, non-punitive manner
            </li>
            <li class="leading-relaxed">
              Provide education for team members to foster a supportive environment
            </li>
            <li class="leading-relaxed">
